<plot>In this Sportscope entry, naturalist 'Van Campen Heilner' (qv) and his wife go to Louisiana bayou country to hunt a particular species of goose. They first use a motorboat and see the local Cajuns trapping muskrats for fur. They later switch to a marsh buggy. After their guide picks out what he believes is a good spot, the three of them set up a blind and set up decoys to lure the geese.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?069065</url></doc>
